          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Sketch the gradient segments for the differential equation $y' = \\frac{x^2}{y^2}$ at the points (1,3), (-2,2), (4,-1), and (0,-2) on the grid below."
        }
      ],
      "parts": null,
      "options": null,
      "answer": {
