          "text": "Differentiate $y = \\tan^{-1} \\sqrt{x}$."
        }
      ],
      "parts": null,
      "options": null,
      "answer": {
        "option_label": null,
        "summary": "$\\frac{1}{2\\sqrt{x}(1 + x)}$",
        "content": [
          {
            "kind": "text",
            "text": "Use chain rule: $\\frac{dy}{dx} = \\frac{1}{1 + (\\sqrt{x})^2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{2\\sqrt{x}} = \\frac{1}{2\\sqrt{x}(1 + x)}$."
          }
        ],
