          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Evaluate $\\int_0^{\\frac{\\pi}{6}} 2 \\sin 2x \\cos x \\, dx$."
        }
      ],
      "parts": null,
      "options": null,
      "answer": {
        "option_label": null,
        "summary": "$\\frac{2}{3}$",
        "content": [
          {
            "kind": "text",
            "text": "Use identity $\\sin 2x = 2\\sin x \\cos x$. Thus, $\\int_0^{\\frac{\\pi}{6}} 4 \\sin x \\cos^2 x \\, dx$. Let $u = \\cos x$, $du = -\\sin x \\, dx$. Evaluate to get $\\frac{2}{3}$."
          }
        ],
